Insider Activity


Individual




Scott J. Reasoner



Mr. Scott J. Reasoner is Senior Vice President-Operations at PDC Energy, Inc.
Mr. Reasoner was previously employed as Vice President-Operations by Patina Oil & Gas Corp. and a Manager-Business Unit by Noble Energy, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the Colorado School of Mines and an MBA from The University of Colorado.



