                                                    New revenue rules mean more work for companies, big revenue for consultants and auditors
                                                


                                                    MarketWatch – 
                                                    6:52 AM ET 07/26/2017
                                                


With less than six months to implement a new revenue rule, companies are scrambling to meet the deadline. The deadline for public companies to implement new revenue recognition rules is less than six months away, but company CFOs and their advisers say the project is getting expensive, messy, and may not be totally over on January 1, 2018.. See also: A revenue rule change is coming and every company will be affected.

















